OL,3,CUK to ban 'sim farms' used by scammers
OL,4,Cto send mass fraud messages
OL,6,FThe Government said the devices are
OL,7,Fused by criminals to hold multiple sim
OL,8,Fcards, which as well as allowing
OL,9,Fscammers to send out thousands of
OL,10,Fmessages to people at the same time,
OL,11,Fcan also be used to create verified
OL,12,Faccounts on social media and other
OL,13,Fplatforms in large volumes.
OL,15,F"The ban announced today is very
OL,16,Fwelcome," said Nick Sharp of the
OL,17,FNational Crime Agency said. "It will
OL,18,Fgive us a vital tool to step up our
OL,19,Ffight against fraudsters, target the
OL,20,Fservices they rely on, and better
OL,21,Fprotect the public
