OL,6,FRachel Andrews, head of corporate
OL,7,Fsecurity at Vodafone UK, said the ban
OL,8,Fon sim farms was an "important step"
OL,9,Fin preventing fraud.
OL,11,F"Vodafone UK is committed to
OL,12,Fprotecting all our customers from
OL,13,Ffraud, including activity enabled by
OL,14,Fsim farms," she said.
OL,16,F"So far this year we have blocked over
OL,17,F38.5 million suspected scam messages,
OL,18,Fand in 2024 that figure reached over
OL,19,F73.5 million for the year.
