OL,6,F"As an industry, UK telecoms operators
OL,7,Fhave blocked more than one billion
OL,8,Fsuspected scam messages since 2023.
OL,10,F"However, we cannot fully tackle fraud
OL,11,Fin isolation; collaboration between
OL,12,Findustry and government is crucial.
OL,14,F"This is a really important step taken
OL,15,Fby the Home Office and we fully
OL,16,Fsupport the inclusion of sim farms in
OL,17,Fthe upcoming legislation.
OL,19,F"We look forward to working together
