OL,6,FShadow home secretary Chris Philp
OL,7,Fsaid: "We welcome this move but let's
OL,8,Fnot pretend Labour led the charge.
OL,9,FThis builds directly on the work the
OL,10,FConservatives did last year to crack
OL,11,Fdown on sim farms through the Criminal
OL,12,FJustice Bill.
OL,14,F"These devices are the weapon of
OL,15,Fchoice for fraudsters. We acted to
OL,16,Fclose that loophole, and it's right
OL,17,Fthat Labour are finally scrambling to
OL,18,Fcatch up.
